860
00:57:03,380 --> 00:57:05,380
[SPEAKER_01] onda skinam kapu svaka čast.

861
00:57:05,380 --> 00:57:08,380
[SPEAKER_01] To je ono što sam najmanje očekivao od svega toga.

862
00:57:08,380 --> 00:57:10,380
[SPEAKER_01] I to je prvi korak prema realizmu.

863
00:57:10,380 --> 00:57:14,380
